    "We couldn't apply that change to the database. Please report this as a bug by [opening a GitHub issue]({{githubIssueLink}}).": "Vi kunne ikke gemme ændringen i databasen. Rapportere venligst denne fejl ved at [åbne en GitHub issue]({{githubIssueLink}}).",
