    "There is already a schedule with this name": "Der findes allerede en tidsplan med dette navn",
    "There is no server configured. After running the server, specify the URL here to use the app. You can always change this later. We will validate that Actual is running at this URL.": "Der er ikke indstillet nogen server. Efter at du har startet serveren, skal du skrive dens URL her for at bruge appen. Du kan altid ændre det senere. Vi kontrollerer, at Actual rent faktisk kører på denne URL.",
    "There was a problem loading one of the chunks of the application. Please reload the page and try again. If the issue persists - there might be an issue with either your internet connection and/or the server where the app is hosted.": "Der opstod et problem da en del af programmet skulle hentes. Genlæs venligst siden og prøv igen. Hvis problemet fortsætter er der muligvis et problem med din internetforbindelse og/eller serveren, hvor appen er hostet.",
